cinnamon-control-center (4.6.2) ulyana; urgency=medium

  [ Michael Webster ]
  * cc-display-panel.c: Use scaled geometry when checking overlap and alignment while dragging.
  * cc-display-panel.c: Realign after a rotation change, re-scale and center the view after a grab ends.
  * cc-display-panel.c: Improve display representation while dragging.
  * cc-display-panel.c: Use a scrolled window in the error popup, and add a reset button to the panel.
  * cc-display-panel.c: Update the view after toggling the fractional scale switch.
  * cc-display-panel.c: Never scale the output width and height.
  * cc-display-panel.c: Fill in all geometry for non-active monitors, not just the size, to ensure uninitialized values don't get returned to callers.
  * cc-display-panel.c: Don't allow monitors to be dragged apart.

  [ Eli Schwartz ]
  * remove outdated build dependency on dbus-glib (#235)

